WEBVTT

00:00:05.040 --> 00:00:08.040
[Mingde Road]

00:00:08.040 --> 00:00:12.920
[Enjoy the winter holidays]

00:00:12.920 --> 00:00:14.805
[Boys Dormitory]

00:00:21.099 --> 00:00:29.300
♪ My passion is like a fire
burning through the desert ♪

00:00:29.300 --> 00:00:30.739
- Going to do laundry?
- Yeah.

00:00:30.739 --> 00:00:31.966
I'll head over first.

00:00:31.966 --> 00:00:33.359
Zhang Shu! Off to play soccer?

00:00:33.359 --> 00:00:35.180
Oh, right. What time is it?

00:00:35.180 --> 00:00:37.408
The China vs. Oman match
should be starting soon, right?

00:00:37.408 --> 00:00:38.579
There's 15 minutes to go.

00:00:38.579 --> 00:00:41.579
15 minutes? Thanks! I gotta run.

00:00:46.960 --> 00:00:48.439
- Yong!
- Lin Wen!

00:00:48.439 --> 00:00:51.200
What are you guys doing?
The China match is about to start!

00:00:51.200 --> 00:00:53.880
You should've said earlier! I totally forgot.

00:00:56.820 --> 00:00:58.639
- Xiao Ming!
- Xiao Ming!

00:00:58.639 --> 00:00:59.979
Where's Yu Lei?

00:00:59.979 --> 00:01:02.699
He's across the hall. Let's go check.

00:01:04.498 --> 00:01:06.080
Yu Lei!

00:01:06.080 --> 00:01:07.919
Yu Lei!

00:01:07.919 --> 00:01:09.279
- What's up?
- Where's Yu Lei?

00:01:09.279 --> 00:01:11.269
- Right here.
- I've got a good feeling

00:01:11.269 --> 00:01:13.360
about today's match.

00:01:13.360 --> 00:01:16.960
Me too. If we win today,
we'll have 14 points total.

00:01:16.960 --> 00:01:19.660
- That means we qualify early!
- Yu Lei, the broadcast is starting.

00:01:19.660 --> 00:01:21.899
What are you still doing? Hurry up!

00:01:21.899 --> 00:01:23.680
Today's match is huge.

00:01:23.680 --> 00:01:25.100
Who wants to just listen to the radio?

00:01:25.100 --> 00:01:27.680
Come on. Let's go watch it on TV
in the duty room.

00:01:27.680 --> 00:01:30.339
I already cleared it with the dorm lady.

00:01:30.339 --> 00:01:31.447
Let's go, everyone!

00:01:31.447 --> 00:01:34.146
- Let's go!
- Let's go watch it together.

00:01:36.460 --> 00:01:38.184
Hurry up!

00:01:38.184 --> 00:01:40.964
- Go, go, go!
- Hurry!

00:01:43.040 --> 00:01:44.400
Wait for me!

00:01:44.400 --> 00:01:46.200
Thanks, ma'am!

00:01:46.920 --> 00:01:47.960
Here.

00:01:47.960 --> 00:01:49.860
Come on, come on.

00:01:52.060 --> 00:01:53.600
Give me one.

00:01:53.600 --> 00:01:55.100
Me too!

00:01:55.100 --> 00:01:56.999
And me!

00:01:56.999 --> 00:01:59.840
- Ready?
- China team! Let's go!

00:01:59.840 --> 00:02:01.640
China team! Let's go!

00:02:01.640 --> 00:02:03.739
China team! Let's go!

00:02:03.739 --> 00:02:05.041
- It's starting!
- Hurry, hurry!

00:02:05.041 --> 00:02:07.619
The Chinese national team,
with a fresh look...

00:02:07.619 --> 00:02:09.519
Who's that?

00:02:14.261 --> 00:02:18.239
The head referee from Singapore
has blown the final whistle!

00:02:18.239 --> 00:02:22.359
China wins at home, 1-0, defeating Oman!

00:02:22.359 --> 00:02:25.239
With this, China has officially qualified!

00:02:25.239 --> 00:02:26.339
That's incredible!

00:02:26.339 --> 00:02:27.580
We qualified!

00:02:27.580 --> 00:02:29.979
China is the best!

00:02:34.220 --> 00:02:38.980
[Students of Mingde University
joyfully celebrate the National Day]

00:02:43.050 --> 00:02:44.519
Students, please calm down!

00:02:44.519 --> 00:02:45.539
Show some restraint!

00:02:45.539 --> 00:02:48.040
Stop smashing your thermoses!

00:02:48.040 --> 00:02:49.739
October 2001.

00:02:49.739 --> 00:02:52.539
China made it to the World Cup
for the first time.

00:02:52.539 --> 00:02:53.820
They say that night,

00:02:53.820 --> 00:02:56.526
hundreds of thermoses
were smashed at Ming University.

00:02:56.526 --> 00:02:58.661
But for me, the way I celebrated

00:02:58.661 --> 00:03:02.100
was heading out into the rain
with my best friends for a game of soccer.

00:03:02.100 --> 00:03:04.608
It was on that muddy field

00:03:04.608 --> 00:03:08.959
that I met the person who would
eventually define my entire youth.

00:03:08.959 --> 00:03:12.739
Have you ever met someone like that
when you were young?

00:03:12.739 --> 00:03:17.900
Someone who doesn't have to do a thing
to make you feel completely outmatched?

00:03:17.900 --> 00:03:23.071
For me, Chen Ke was that person.

00:03:23.071 --> 00:03:24.871
Come on!

00:03:26.950 --> 00:03:36.970
Timing and Subtitles provided to you
by 💥🍥 TEAM 7️⃣ 🍥💥 @viki.com

00:03:41.060 --> 00:03:42.359
Come on, Chen Ke!

00:03:42.359 --> 00:03:43.900
Let's play!

00:03:43.900 --> 00:03:45.660
Yu Lei, are you crazy?

00:03:45.660 --> 00:03:48.639
The ground is still soaked.
You really want to play now?

00:03:48.639 --> 00:03:51.319
Come on! Let's be crazy together!

00:03:53.320 --> 00:03:57.660
We met, fell in love,
and truly got to know each other.

00:03:57.660 --> 00:03:59.040
But don't get the wrong idea.

00:03:59.040 --> 00:04:01.620
Our beginning wasn't exactly romantic.

00:04:01.620 --> 00:04:05.579
Back then, I thought this guy named Chen Ke
was cold, arrogant,

00:04:05.579 --> 00:04:09.340
and clearly destined to be my rival.

00:04:09.340 --> 00:04:13.880
It wasn't until much later that I realized
he was the only answer

00:04:13.880 --> 00:04:16.030
to all the questions of my youth.

00:04:22.000 --> 00:04:26.040
[Episode 1: Let's Make a Real Bet]

00:04:26.040 --> 00:04:27.386
The sky is clear,

00:04:27.386 --> 00:04:29.020
the autumn breeze is cool,
[Students today, pillars tomorrow]

00:04:29.020 --> 00:04:32.100
and students come from all over.
[Students today, pillars tomorrow]

00:04:32.100 --> 00:04:35.320
They are joining our campus
to pursue their dreams.

00:04:35.320 --> 00:04:37.760
It is an honor to meet you all
[A new start, the class of 2000]

00:04:37.760 --> 00:04:40.478
at the beautiful Mingde University,
[your dream starts here]

00:04:40.478 --> 00:04:44.060
and share in the joy of this new beginning.

00:04:46.239 --> 00:04:48.699
Dad! Hurry up!

00:04:51.339 --> 00:04:53.620
You little brat.

00:04:58.419 --> 00:05:00.500
August 27, 2000.

00:05:00.500 --> 00:05:01.740
Sunny.

00:05:01.740 --> 00:05:04.520
This was my first day at Mingde University.

00:05:04.520 --> 00:05:06.650
And on that same day,

00:05:06.650 --> 00:05:11.520
a reckless boy clumsily crashed into my life.

00:05:20.579 --> 00:05:22.980
Hey! Can you kick the ball back?

00:05:22.980 --> 00:05:24.760
Sure.

00:05:24.760 --> 00:05:26.360
Watch out!

00:05:42.899 --> 00:05:44.260
I'm so sorry!

00:05:44.260 --> 00:05:45.920
I didn't mean to.

00:05:45.920 --> 00:05:47.505
Your clothes got dirty.

00:05:47.505 --> 00:05:48.970
Let me help you clean it off.

00:05:48.970 --> 00:05:50.770
It's fine.

00:05:54.167 --> 00:05:58.200
Wait, I'm trying to help, and you're annoyed?

00:05:58.200 --> 00:06:00.300
Talk about being difficult.

00:06:00.300 --> 00:06:01.559
You brat.

00:06:01.559 --> 00:06:03.699
You're a college student now,
try not to be so clumsy.

00:06:03.699 --> 00:06:06.760
Dad, school hasn't even
officially started yet.

00:06:06.760 --> 00:06:08.313
Look at that student over there.

00:06:08.313 --> 00:06:11.223
He didn't even bring his parents.
He's carrying all his own luggage.

00:06:11.223 --> 00:06:12.339
Look at you.

00:06:12.339 --> 00:06:13.600
Here, take this.

00:06:13.600 --> 00:06:16.470
- You're the one who insisted on coming.
- Let's go.

00:06:50.819 --> 00:06:53.740
- Who are you?
- Hi! I'm Yu Lei.

00:06:53.740 --> 00:06:56.139
I'm in Room 301 too.

00:06:56.139 --> 00:06:58.319
- So you're Yu Lei?
- Yeah.

00:06:58.319 --> 00:07:00.749
Does your family own a submarine
or something?

00:07:00.749 --> 00:07:03.658
They gave you a name like that.
(*His name sounds like "torpedo")

00:07:03.658 --> 00:07:05.400
I'm Li Ming. I'm a sprinter.

00:07:05.400 --> 00:07:07.060
From now on,
we should look out for each other.

00:07:07.060 --> 00:07:08.180
Of course.

00:07:08.180 --> 00:07:10.019
Alright, you're here.

00:07:10.019 --> 00:07:12.300
Looks like the whole room is finally here.

00:07:12.300 --> 00:07:14.560
Come on. I'll show you your bunk.

00:07:14.560 --> 00:07:16.639
Okay. Thanks.

00:07:22.857 --> 00:07:25.639
Hi. I'm He Jin.

00:07:25.639 --> 00:07:27.259
[No. 1, Chen Ke, Economic Law, Class A]
We're roommates now.

00:07:27.259 --> 00:07:29.159
I'm Chen Ke.

00:07:31.881 --> 00:07:34.640
I think this is my bunk.

00:07:34.640 --> 00:07:35.960
Oh, sorry. I must have misread it.

00:07:35.960 --> 00:07:37.420
I must have misread it.

00:07:37.420 --> 00:07:40.139
Actually, I've always slept by the window.

00:07:40.139 --> 00:07:42.340
Do you mind if we switch?

00:07:43.359 --> 00:07:44.860
I don't think that's a good idea.

00:07:44.860 --> 00:07:47.239
The school has already assigned them.

00:07:47.239 --> 00:07:49.620
Oh, okay. Sorry about that.

00:08:12.699 --> 00:08:14.720
By the way, it's already lunchtime.

00:08:14.720 --> 00:08:17.939
Why don't we all go grab a bite?

00:08:17.939 --> 00:08:19.492
Sure.

00:08:24.080 --> 00:08:28.019
I didn't expect
only the two of us to show up today.

00:08:29.440 --> 00:08:33.100
The other two might be locals.

00:08:33.100 --> 00:08:35.239
They probably won't arrive until later.

00:08:35.239 --> 00:08:37.039
Probably.

00:08:39.220 --> 00:08:41.019
Hey, you should try some of mine.

00:08:41.019 --> 00:08:44.040
This braised pork is really good.

00:08:44.040 --> 00:08:45.940
No thanks.
Braised pork is too greasy for me.

00:08:45.940 --> 00:08:47.740
I'm not used to it.

00:08:50.300 --> 00:08:52.499
There's a made-to-order stall over there.

00:08:52.499 --> 00:08:53.866
Check the menu.

00:08:53.866 --> 00:08:57.560
Maybe we can go get a side of greens.

00:08:57.560 --> 00:08:58.639
Don't bother.

00:08:58.639 --> 00:09:00.280
But thanks.

00:09:00.280 --> 00:09:01.780
Alright.

00:09:03.160 --> 00:09:06.560
So, do you play soccer?

00:09:06.560 --> 00:09:08.139
Yeah.

00:09:08.139 --> 00:09:12.200
If you're free this afternoon,
let's go kick the ball around.

00:09:13.699 --> 00:09:15.199
Okay.

00:09:23.320 --> 00:09:24.560
Come on, come on!

00:09:24.560 --> 00:09:26.119
- Let's drink!
- Cheers!

00:09:26.119 --> 00:09:28.019
Cheers!

00:09:31.860 --> 00:09:34.719
Not bad, man. Impressive.

00:09:36.460 --> 00:09:38.161
Look, here's the deal.

00:09:38.161 --> 00:09:39.899
I've been here training for a month already.

00:09:39.900 --> 00:09:42.640
If you have any questions about the school, just ask me.

00:09:42.640 --> 00:09:43.710
Alright?

00:09:43.710 --> 00:09:47.539
I heard the public showers on campus
don't have any stalls.

00:09:47.539 --> 00:09:49.239
Is that true?

00:09:52.100 --> 00:09:54.539
It's true? Then everyone's just... exposed?

00:09:54.539 --> 00:09:57.119
It's a shower. Everyone's naked anyway.

00:09:57.119 --> 00:09:59.139
What's there to see?

00:10:00.580 --> 00:10:03.239
That's not the point.

00:10:03.239 --> 00:10:07.279
Now, if it were girls naked,
that would be something to see.

00:10:11.419 --> 00:10:16.999
Brother, you clearly haven't experienced
the bathhouse scrub-masters yet.

00:10:16.999 --> 00:10:19.080
I highly recommend it.

00:10:19.080 --> 00:10:21.280
You just lie there on the table,

00:10:21.280 --> 00:10:24.739
and the master scrubs you down like crazy.

00:10:24.739 --> 00:10:26.539
It feels amazing.

00:10:27.440 --> 00:10:30.860
Wait, how do they scrub you?

00:10:30.860 --> 00:10:32.300
Like, your whole body?

00:10:32.300 --> 00:10:34.040
Yep.

00:10:34.040 --> 00:10:35.659
From head to toe.

00:10:35.659 --> 00:10:37.400
Inside and out.

00:10:37.400 --> 00:10:40.280
They'll scrub every single nook and cranny
until you're squeaky clean.

00:10:40.280 --> 00:10:42.659
Wanna give me a scrub?

00:10:42.659 --> 00:10:43.999
Look at you.

00:10:43.999 --> 00:10:45.900
Come on. Drink up!

00:10:45.900 --> 00:10:48.820
- Come.
- Liar.

00:10:53.839 --> 00:10:58.580
Alright. Let's head back to the dorm!

00:10:58.580 --> 00:11:02.879
Guys, we got everything we need, right?

00:11:02.879 --> 00:11:03.880
How about this?

00:11:03.880 --> 00:11:08.539
Since I'm free, let's find an internet cafe
and play some Starcraft.

00:11:08.539 --> 00:11:10.580
Maybe another day.

00:11:10.580 --> 00:11:12.839
I've been unpacking all day.

00:11:12.839 --> 00:11:16.979
Right now,
I just want to go back and lie down.

00:11:16.979 --> 00:11:19.019
What's wrong with you?

00:11:19.019 --> 00:11:21.860
You're too young to be this weak.

00:11:21.860 --> 00:11:25.719
Do you want me to give you a leg massage
to help you relax?

00:11:25.719 --> 00:11:27.301
Get away from me, you creep.

00:11:27.301 --> 00:11:29.639
Look at you.

00:11:50.160 --> 00:11:51.759
What are you looking at?

00:11:51.759 --> 00:11:53.359
A beautiful girl.

00:11:53.359 --> 00:11:54.519
A beauty?

00:11:54.519 --> 00:11:55.960
- You're right.
- Sis?

00:11:55.960 --> 00:11:58.139
I'm gonna go get her number.

00:11:58.139 --> 00:11:59.459
What are you shouting for?

00:11:59.459 --> 00:12:01.759
That's my sister.

00:12:01.759 --> 00:12:02.879
Your sister?

00:12:02.879 --> 00:12:04.840
Your sister?

00:12:08.080 --> 00:12:10.560
- Thanks.
- No problem.

00:12:10.560 --> 00:12:11.719
You're Chen Ke, right?

00:12:11.719 --> 00:12:14.280
A freshman at the Law School?

00:12:14.280 --> 00:12:16.080
Yes. And you are?

00:12:16.080 --> 00:12:18.100
We met at the registration desk today.

00:12:18.100 --> 00:12:19.599
I'm Zhang Han.

00:12:19.599 --> 00:12:22.019
Sis! What are you doing here?

00:12:22.019 --> 00:12:23.619
I just went to your dorm
but couldn't find you.

00:12:23.619 --> 00:12:25.940
I didn't expect to run into you here.

00:12:25.940 --> 00:12:29.000
Let's go, Sis. I have so much to tell you.

00:12:32.400 --> 00:12:34.359
Sis, you had the whole day.

00:12:34.359 --> 00:12:36.260
Why did it take you so long to find me?

00:12:36.260 --> 00:12:38.239
I was just elected Student Union President.

00:12:38.239 --> 00:12:40.340
I've been busy welcoming freshmen all day.

00:12:40.340 --> 00:12:41.960
I just finished.

00:12:41.960 --> 00:12:44.300
So, Lei, is your dorm all set up?

00:12:44.300 --> 00:12:46.999
It's fine.
I've finished organizing everything.

00:12:46.999 --> 00:12:48.239
The school mattresses are thin.

00:12:48.239 --> 00:12:50.960
I figured you wouldn't be comfortable,
so I bought you a new one.

00:12:50.960 --> 00:12:53.879
You weren't in your room,
so I left it with the dorm lady.

00:12:53.879 --> 00:12:57.280
- Don't forget to pick it up.
- Okay, thanks Sis.

00:12:57.280 --> 00:12:59.619
If you need anything else, just let me know.

00:12:59.619 --> 00:13:01.320
I'm all set.

00:13:01.320 --> 00:13:04.759
Mom and Dad even bought extra stuff
for me to bring to you.

00:13:04.759 --> 00:13:07.125
- Hello, senior.
- Hi.

00:13:07.999 --> 00:13:09.359
That's good then.

00:13:09.359 --> 00:13:11.700
What are you looking at?

00:13:11.700 --> 00:13:14.639
- Are you getting along with your roommates?
- Of course.

00:13:14.639 --> 00:13:16.560
Your brother is handsome and smart.

00:13:16.560 --> 00:13:18.619
Everyone loves me.
Even the flowers bloom when I walk by.

00:13:18.619 --> 00:13:21.239
See? They're blooming right now.

00:13:21.239 --> 00:13:24.200
Don't worry. I'll do great anywhere.

00:13:24.739 --> 00:13:28.080
This is Mingde University. There are talented people everywhere.

00:13:28.080 --> 00:13:30.779
Don't be so arrogant.

00:13:30.779 --> 00:13:32.739
Who's being arrogant?

00:13:32.739 --> 00:13:35.160
I was the top scorer in the city
on the entrance exam.

00:13:35.160 --> 00:13:37.519
Could there really be
someone better than me?

00:13:37.519 --> 00:13:40.800
Where? Where are they?

00:13:40.800 --> 00:13:43.400
There you go again.

00:13:43.400 --> 00:13:47.359
In your class alone,
there's someone with better grades than you.

00:13:47.359 --> 00:13:48.820
Really?

00:13:48.820 --> 00:13:49.920
I don't believe it.

00:13:49.920 --> 00:13:52.587
Why would I lie? In your class, there's someone named Chen Ke.

00:13:52.587 --> 00:13:56.319
His entrance exam score
was the highest in the entire Law School.

00:13:56.319 --> 00:13:58.460
There's always someone better.
The world is bigger than you think.

00:13:58.460 --> 00:14:01.739
Try to be a little more humble.

00:14:01.739 --> 00:14:04.340
So my class has someone like that?

00:14:04.340 --> 00:14:06.160
I'll have to see it for myself.

00:14:06.160 --> 00:14:07.999
You've already met him.

00:14:07.999 --> 00:14:10.080
The boy I was just talking to.

00:14:10.080 --> 00:14:11.619
What?

00:14:11.619 --> 00:14:13.719
Him?

00:14:16.280 --> 00:14:19.259
Hello, everyone.

00:14:23.239 --> 00:14:26.100
Welcome to the Economic Law program.

00:14:26.100 --> 00:14:29.680
This semester, each of you
has a blank sheet of paper before you.

00:14:29.680 --> 00:14:31.177
Chen Ke.

00:14:31.177 --> 00:14:34.997
If you choose hard work and perseverance,

00:14:34.997 --> 00:14:39.639
then you will find success and fulfillment.

00:14:39.639 --> 00:14:43.239
But if you choose laziness and retreating,

00:14:43.239 --> 00:14:44.900
- then what awaits you...
- Height...

00:14:44.900 --> 00:14:47.499
- will still be a blank sheet of paper.
- About 180 cm.

00:14:47.499 --> 00:14:50.080
- Not as tall as me.
- A good start is the beginning of success.

00:14:50.080 --> 00:14:51.960
Entrance exam score...

00:14:51.960 --> 00:14:55.139
- You are at a point in your lives...
- A bit better than me.

00:14:55.139 --> 00:14:57.341
- You can become a new version of yourselves.
- Who are you drawing?

00:14:57.341 --> 00:15:00.161
- Does everyone believe in themselves?
- Yes!

00:15:00.161 --> 00:15:02.559
Give yourselves a round of applause.

00:15:05.879 --> 00:15:10.200
Alright, students.
Next, let's have another warm welcome.

00:15:10.200 --> 00:15:14.539
Chen Ke, please come up
and introduce yourself.

00:15:19.619 --> 00:15:21.440
Hi everyone, I'm Chen Ke.

00:15:21.440 --> 00:15:23.739
C-H-E-N K-E.

00:15:23.739 --> 00:15:24.860
I live by the sea.

00:15:24.860 --> 00:15:29.580
I build model ships, read manga,
and play soccer.

00:15:29.580 --> 00:15:31.139
Nothing special about him.

00:15:31.139 --> 00:15:33.419
Just a bookworm.

00:15:36.940 --> 00:15:42.619
And now, let's welcome Yu Lei
to introduce himself.

00:15:46.220 --> 00:15:48.300
Hi everyone. I'm Yu Lei.

00:15:48.300 --> 00:15:49.940
It's not 'Torpedo' like the weapon.

00:15:49.940 --> 00:15:52.820
It's 'Yu' as in 'equal to',
and 'Lei' as in 'thunder'.

00:15:52.820 --> 00:15:56.580
I love sports, gaming, and anime.

00:15:56.580 --> 00:16:00.940
If anyone wants to play CS
or needs someone for soccer,

00:16:00.940 --> 00:16:02.800
just let me know.

00:16:02.800 --> 00:16:04.776
Thanks.

00:16:10.720 --> 00:16:13.019
Youth should look like youth.

00:16:13.019 --> 00:16:16.739
We should let our youth bloom to the fullest.

00:16:18.899 --> 00:16:20.940
Students, time is short.

00:16:20.940 --> 00:16:25.940
Next, we need to choose a student
from our class

00:16:25.940 --> 00:16:28.980
to be in charge of class affairs
this semester.

00:16:28.980 --> 00:16:31.139
Does anyone want to volunteer?

00:16:31.139 --> 00:16:33.899
Professor, how about me?

00:16:33.899 --> 00:16:35.980
Yu Lei.

00:16:35.980 --> 00:16:39.060
Does everyone think
Yu Lei is up for the task?

00:16:39.060 --> 00:16:40.460
Yes!

00:16:40.460 --> 00:16:42.460
Good!

00:16:43.239 --> 00:16:47.280
Then for this semester,
Yu Lei will be our class monitor.

00:16:47.280 --> 00:16:52.019
I hope Yu Lei will work hard and contribute
to our class community.

00:16:52.019 --> 00:16:54.700
Let's give another round of applause
to Yu Lei.

00:16:54.700 --> 00:16:58.399
- No problem.
- Let's give him another hand.

00:17:08.219 --> 00:17:12.020
Yu Lei, are you sure you
don't want to shower with us?

00:17:12.020 --> 00:17:13.440
No thanks.

00:17:13.440 --> 00:17:16.979
You guys go ahead.
I'll just wash up here.

00:17:16.979 --> 00:17:19.739
- Alright, we're heading out.
- Okay.

00:17:23.440 --> 00:17:26.139
What's the deal with Chen Ke?

00:17:26.139 --> 00:17:28.920
Why is my sister so interested in him?

00:17:33.360 --> 00:17:40.440
♪ Love is love,
no need to be generous with feelings ♪

00:17:40.440 --> 00:17:44.379
♪ No one needs to give me a golden age ♪

00:17:44.379 --> 00:17:48.260
♪ I want you right now ♪

00:17:53.120 --> 00:17:56.200
I'm clearly the most handsome
and talented one here.

00:18:10.219 --> 00:18:13.139
Hey, your washbasin.

00:18:31.740 --> 00:18:34.419
Wasn't that Chen Ke just now?

00:18:37.053 --> 00:18:39.053
What bad luck.

00:18:44.139 --> 00:18:45.712
This is so annoying.

00:18:45.712 --> 00:18:47.175
[Thunder]
My sister actually thinks

00:18:47.175 --> 00:18:48.859
Chen Ke is better than me.

00:18:48.859 --> 00:18:50.927
[O-O]
Who is Chen Ke?

00:18:53.100 --> 00:18:55.600
[Thunder]
Just a guy acting all deep.

00:18:55.600 --> 00:18:58.359
What's so great about him?

00:18:58.999 --> 00:19:01.060
He had that sour face on registration day.

00:19:01.060 --> 00:19:03.020
So unapproachable.

00:19:03.020 --> 00:19:06.260
And yet my sister remembered his name.

00:19:07.540 --> 00:19:10.139
His introduction in class was so dry too.

00:19:10.139 --> 00:19:12.239
Total bookworm.

00:19:13.060 --> 00:19:15.440
He ignores his roommates too.

00:19:15.440 --> 00:19:17.500
Clearly, he's not very popular.

00:19:17.500 --> 00:19:20.020
I'm definitely the coolest one.

00:19:20.020 --> 00:19:22.020
Yeah!

00:19:26.300 --> 00:19:28.619
Xiao Ming, when did you get back?

00:19:28.619 --> 00:19:31.120
I've been standing here
watching you for a while.

00:19:31.120 --> 00:19:34.400
Just watching you grin
while chatting with girls.

00:19:41.940 --> 00:19:44.139
I'm the one who backed you up
for class monitor!

00:19:44.139 --> 00:19:45.279
Is this how you repay me?

00:19:45.279 --> 00:19:47.239
You won't introduce me to your pretty cousin,

00:19:47.239 --> 00:19:50.219
and now you're sneaking around
chatting with girls online.

00:19:50.219 --> 00:19:52.780
Keeping them all to yourself
is shameful, you know?

00:19:52.780 --> 00:19:54.540
Xiao Ming, you've got it all wrong!

00:19:54.540 --> 00:19:56.042
- Let me explain.
- Explain?

00:19:56.042 --> 00:19:57.080
Explaining is covering it up.

00:19:57.080 --> 00:19:58.619
And covering it up
means it's definitely true.

00:19:58.619 --> 00:20:02.300
Save it. I sentence you to death by hanging,
effective immediately.

00:20:02.300 --> 00:20:03.960
Xiao Ming, Xiao Ming!

00:20:03.960 --> 00:20:05.060
I've got things to do.

00:20:05.060 --> 00:20:07.840
I'll introduce you next time, okay?

00:20:08.619 --> 00:20:10.779
You better not be messing with me.

00:20:11.875 --> 00:20:15.120
[Mingde University Club New Recruiting Area]

00:20:15.120 --> 00:20:16.519
Hey, come join us!

00:20:16.519 --> 00:20:18.580
Come take a look!
Street Dance Club recruitment!

00:20:18.580 --> 00:20:19.961
Check it out, everyone!

00:20:19.961 --> 00:20:22.111
Street Dance Club is welcoming new members!
Come on, come on!

00:20:22.111 --> 00:20:23.920
[Swing away at the Baseball Club]
Join the Street Dance Club!

00:20:23.920 --> 00:20:26.519
Anyone want to learn how to street dance?

00:20:26.519 --> 00:20:28.181
- Learn about our Baseball Club!
- Everyone!

00:20:28.181 --> 00:20:30.079
Come on, come on!

00:20:30.079 --> 00:20:32.899
Hey beautiful, want to learn street dance?

00:20:32.899 --> 00:20:35.179
Ladies, come learn street dance!

00:20:35.179 --> 00:20:38.987
Take a look, everyone!
Street Dance Club recruitment!

00:20:38.987 --> 00:20:41.983
[The History Research Club is really strong]

00:20:41.983 --> 00:20:43.840
Hey, Thunder.

00:21:07.060 --> 00:21:09.020
O-O?

00:21:09.020 --> 00:21:11.635
Wait, you're a guy?

00:21:11.635 --> 00:21:13.878
I never said I was a girl.

00:21:13.878 --> 00:21:16.060
I just thought...

00:21:18.519 --> 00:21:20.840
Great souls were always androgynous.

00:21:20.840 --> 00:21:22.139
If that's how you see me,

00:21:22.139 --> 00:21:26.379
I'll take it as a compliment to my soul.

00:21:26.379 --> 00:21:30.260
So, does that mean you've fallen for me?

00:21:30.260 --> 00:21:33.619
Me? Don't talk nonsense. I have not.

00:21:34.336 --> 00:21:36.612
Since our souls resonated online,

00:21:36.612 --> 00:21:39.759
I'm sure we'll have some chemistry
in real life too.

00:21:39.759 --> 00:21:42.279
Thunder, I'm fine with it.

00:21:42.279 --> 00:21:43.540
Stop making excuses.

00:21:43.540 --> 00:21:46.279
I'm not! Don't go ruining my reputation.

00:21:46.279 --> 00:21:49.440
Besides, opposites attract, like poles repel.

00:21:49.440 --> 00:21:51.840
Did you even pass middle school physics?

00:21:53.379 --> 00:21:55.700
Drama Club...

00:21:55.700 --> 00:21:58.802
- Comedy Club...
- Check out the Comedy Club.

00:22:00.340 --> 00:22:02.020
We even have a Baseball Club.

00:22:02.020 --> 00:22:04.020
That's pretty trendy.

00:22:04.799 --> 00:22:05.939
What is he doing here?

00:22:05.939 --> 00:22:07.279
Who?

00:22:07.279 --> 00:22:10.213
That annoying guy, Chen Ke.

00:22:10.213 --> 00:22:12.179
What a buzzkill.

00:22:14.540 --> 00:22:16.699
Yu Lei, what a coincidence.

00:22:16.699 --> 00:22:18.200
Yeah, just checking things out.

00:22:18.200 --> 00:22:21.200
Are you interested in baseball too?

00:22:21.200 --> 00:22:23.139
It's alright.

00:22:24.740 --> 00:22:27.960
Lei, how come you didn't tell me
you became class monitor?

00:22:27.960 --> 00:22:30.979
Sis, I was just about to go find you
at the Student Union booth.

00:22:30.979 --> 00:22:32.460
I wanted to surprise you.

00:22:32.460 --> 00:22:34.355
Alright.

00:22:34.939 --> 00:22:37.440
Chen Ke, I was looking for you.

00:22:37.440 --> 00:22:38.799
Senior?

00:22:38.799 --> 00:22:41.200
The school is hosting a freshman gala.

00:22:41.200 --> 00:22:43.139
I know you're a Level 10 pianist.

00:22:43.139 --> 00:22:45.540
Would you be interested in
representing the Law School

00:22:45.540 --> 00:22:47.540
with a performance?

00:22:49.099 --> 00:22:50.559
Are you jealous?

00:22:50.559 --> 00:22:52.899
And you say you don't have a sister complex.

00:22:52.899 --> 00:22:54.279
Shut up.

00:22:54.279 --> 00:22:56.448
It's not like that.

00:22:56.448 --> 00:22:58.219
Sure, I'll do it.

00:22:58.219 --> 00:23:01.699
Great! I'll go get the application form
for you.

00:23:17.239 --> 00:23:19.480
You can even skip stones?

00:23:21.020 --> 00:23:22.720
Tell me.

00:23:24.400 --> 00:23:27.939
Is playing the piano really that impressive?

00:23:29.979 --> 00:23:32.319
Playing at level 10?

00:23:32.319 --> 00:23:34.839
Yeah, that's actually very impressive.

00:23:37.419 --> 00:23:40.840
But I became class monitor,
which is a big deal,

00:23:40.840 --> 00:23:42.740
and she barely said anything.

00:23:42.740 --> 00:23:45.580
Then she turns around
and only cares about Chen Ke.

00:23:47.459 --> 00:23:49.859
Must be that chemistry I mentioned.

00:23:49.859 --> 00:23:51.239
You...

00:23:51.239 --> 00:23:53.840
To prepare for the 2000 Asian Cup,

00:23:53.840 --> 00:23:59.360
the China men's soccer team plans to play
several friendly warm-up matches.

00:23:59.360 --> 00:24:00.719
That's it!

00:24:00.719 --> 00:24:03.540
I'm definitely going to get even.

00:24:06.860 --> 00:24:11.240
Guys! Room 301 actually sent us a challenge!

00:24:12.759 --> 00:24:15.440
"To celebrate the 2000 Asian Cup,

00:24:15.440 --> 00:24:20.279
Room 301 invites Room 312
to a 4-on-4 friendly soccer match."

00:24:20.279 --> 00:24:22.300
"Friendship first, competition second."

00:24:22.300 --> 00:24:24.999
"Losers buy the winners Cokes."

00:24:24.999 --> 00:24:27.475
This is so sudden. And surprisingly formal.

00:24:27.475 --> 00:24:28.500
I have no idea either.

00:24:28.500 --> 00:24:31.680
As soon as I got back,
Yu Lei from 301 handed me this challenge.

00:24:31.680 --> 00:24:33.820
So, guys, should we accept?

00:24:33.820 --> 00:24:35.780
We're already here. Why not?

00:24:35.780 --> 00:24:37.580
What do you think, Chen Ke?

00:24:37.580 --> 00:24:39.060
It's just a friendly match.

00:24:39.060 --> 00:24:40.500
Let's play.

00:24:40.500 --> 00:24:42.100
Alright, let's do it.

00:24:42.100 --> 00:24:44.680
Let's show them what Room 312 is made of.

00:24:44.680 --> 00:24:46.100
We'll crush them!

00:24:46.100 --> 00:24:47.820
Yeah, crush them!

00:24:47.820 --> 00:24:49.239
Come on, guys!

00:24:49.239 --> 00:24:50.279
312... Victory!

00:24:50.279 --> 00:24:52.079
Victory!

00:24:54.279 --> 00:24:57.179
President, I've decided on my piece
for the gala.

00:24:57.179 --> 00:24:58.899
Here's the form.

00:24:58.899 --> 00:25:00.580
Moonlight Sonata?

00:25:00.580 --> 00:25:02.039
I'm looking forward to it.

00:25:02.039 --> 00:25:03.219
Thank you, President.

00:25:03.219 --> 00:25:04.400
Stop calling me President.

00:25:04.400 --> 00:25:05.759
It sounds so weird.

00:25:05.759 --> 00:25:09.600
Just use my name, or call me 'Senior'.

00:25:09.600 --> 00:25:12.580
Okay. Thanks, Senior.

00:25:18.379 --> 00:25:20.659
Sis! I want to sign up for the gala too.

00:25:20.659 --> 00:25:22.020
Show some respect.

00:25:22.020 --> 00:25:23.640
Call me President.

00:25:23.640 --> 00:25:27.239
Fine. President Zhang.

00:25:27.239 --> 00:25:30.219
Didn't you say you were sick of hosting galas

00:25:30.219 --> 00:25:31.619
after doing it for three years
in high school?

00:25:31.619 --> 00:25:33.300
That was then.

00:25:33.300 --> 00:25:37.139
Besides, college is different
from high school.

00:25:37.139 --> 00:25:39.979
I need to make a grand entrance.

00:25:40.680 --> 00:25:42.759
Tone it down a bit.

00:25:42.759 --> 00:25:44.500
Auditions are next week.

00:25:44.500 --> 00:25:46.840
You two better be prepared.

00:25:46.840 --> 00:25:49.619
- Okay.
- Yes, ma'am!

00:25:49.619 --> 00:25:52.339
By the way, Chen Ke,
about the match this afternoon,

00:25:52.339 --> 00:25:55.039
don't let Room 312 chicken out.

00:25:55.039 --> 00:25:56.360
We won't.

00:25:56.360 --> 00:25:58.279
You guys are playing soccer today?

00:25:58.279 --> 00:26:02.020
Yeah, Sis. Us Room 301 challenged them
to a friendly match.

00:26:02.020 --> 00:26:04.156
You should come watch!

00:26:04.156 --> 00:26:07.139
I'm busy this afternoon
with Student Union gala prep.

00:26:07.139 --> 00:26:09.979
- I can't make it.
- Oh, okay.

00:26:09.979 --> 00:26:12.139
Lei, take it easy out there.

00:26:12.139 --> 00:26:13.580
Don't go getting injured
right at the start of the term.

00:26:13.580 --> 00:26:14.659
I know.

00:26:14.659 --> 00:26:18.163
Chen Ke, go easy on our Yu Lei, okay?

00:26:19.160 --> 00:26:20.640
No problem.

00:26:20.640 --> 00:26:24.280
Sis! I don't need him to go easy on me.

00:26:44.360 --> 00:26:46.239
Didn't you say your sister
was coming to watch us play?

00:26:46.239 --> 00:26:47.339
Where is she?

00:26:47.339 --> 00:26:48.459
I asked her.

00:26:48.459 --> 00:26:49.560
I really did.

00:26:49.560 --> 00:26:51.400
She's just too busy with the Student Union.

00:26:51.400 --> 00:26:53.960
- You...
- Look over there. See?

00:26:53.960 --> 00:26:56.179
- There are plenty of other spectators.
- So handsome!

00:26:56.179 --> 00:26:59.281
Take a good look.
What kind of spectators are those?

00:27:00.720 --> 00:27:02.665
I specially came to watch.

00:27:02.665 --> 00:27:04.705
Go Yu Lei!

00:27:06.559 --> 00:27:08.100
Li Ming!

00:27:12.680 --> 00:27:15.619
Legs feeling weak without any girls around?

00:27:15.619 --> 00:27:17.279
Shut it, Liu Hai Bin!

00:27:17.279 --> 00:27:20.580
Even on my worst day,
I can still outrun a shot-putter like you.

00:27:20.580 --> 00:27:21.799
Right, guys?

00:27:21.799 --> 00:27:23.680
Right!

00:27:26.559 --> 00:27:28.440
What's the use of being fast?

00:27:28.440 --> 00:27:30.139
You actually have to score!

00:27:30.139 --> 00:27:32.419
My roommates aren't exactly pushovers.

00:27:32.419 --> 00:27:37.659
Well, sorry to say, but today,
you're going home with a big fat zero.

00:28:09.079 --> 00:28:10.879
Go!

00:28:12.859 --> 00:28:14.659
Get the ball!

00:28:14.659 --> 00:28:17.340
- Break through the middle!
- Pass it! Pass it!

00:28:19.319 --> 00:28:21.219
Run!

00:28:41.057 --> 00:28:42.957
Here, have some water.

00:28:48.239 --> 00:28:49.676
He's barely even sweating.

00:28:49.676 --> 00:28:51.699
Is he looking down on me?

00:28:51.699 --> 00:28:53.100
Next half, we'll play man-to-man.

00:28:53.100 --> 00:28:54.219
You go mark him.

00:28:54.219 --> 00:28:56.720
Maybe.

00:28:57.300 --> 00:28:59.459
Lei, take it easy out there.

00:28:59.459 --> 00:29:00.740
Don't go getting injured
right at the start of the term.

00:29:00.740 --> 00:29:01.979
I know.

00:29:01.979 --> 00:29:04.939
Chen Ke, go easy on our Yu Lei, okay?

00:29:04.939 --> 00:29:06.739
No problem.

00:29:11.979 --> 00:29:14.925
Sorry, I need to talk to Chen Ke
for a second.

00:29:15.475 --> 00:29:16.719
What's going on?

00:29:16.719 --> 00:29:18.419
No idea.

00:29:19.759 --> 00:29:21.740
Can you take this game seriously?

00:29:21.740 --> 00:29:23.300
I am taking it seriously.

00:29:23.300 --> 00:29:26.179
Besides, it's just a friendly match.

00:29:26.979 --> 00:29:29.020
Do you think betting just Cokes is boring?

00:29:29.020 --> 00:29:30.300
Then let's make a real bet.

00:29:30.300 --> 00:29:33.899
Whoever loses can't talk to Zhang Han
for a month.

00:29:56.260 --> 00:29:57.519
Chen Ke is so cool!

00:29:57.519 --> 00:29:59.239
Chen Ke is amazing!

00:29:59.239 --> 00:30:00.799
What a goal!

00:30:00.799 --> 00:30:03.139
It's 1-0!

00:30:03.139 --> 00:30:04.519
What's the rush?

00:30:04.519 --> 00:30:06.440
The ball is round, anything can happen.

00:30:06.440 --> 00:30:09.279
Give it a rest.
Just get ready to buy us those Cokes.

00:30:09.279 --> 00:30:11.219
You just wait.

00:30:36.840 --> 00:30:38.033
Did you do that on purpose?

00:30:38.033 --> 00:30:39.379
- Xiao Ming, Xiao Ming!
- Play the ball, not the man!

00:30:39.379 --> 00:30:40.840
- Don't do anything stupid!
- Calm down, calm down!

00:30:40.840 --> 00:30:42.699
- Don't lose your head! Calm down!
- I didn't mean it.

00:30:42.699 --> 00:30:44.419
Yu Lei, are you okay?

00:30:44.419 --> 00:30:46.139
I was just defending normally.

00:30:46.139 --> 00:30:47.439
Who knew...

00:30:47.439 --> 00:30:48.894
- You have some nerve!
- Don't do anything stupid!

00:30:48.894 --> 00:30:51.319
- Wait...
- I really didn't mean it.

00:30:51.319 --> 00:30:52.300
Stop shouting, everyone!

00:30:52.300 --> 00:30:54.760
Let me see how bad it is.

00:30:55.619 --> 00:30:57.279
Do you know what you're doing?

00:30:57.279 --> 00:30:59.319
Yeah, I have experience with this.

00:30:59.319 --> 00:31:01.260
It's fine, I don't need...

00:31:01.260 --> 00:31:03.260
Just leave me alone.

00:31:03.960 --> 00:31:05.440
It's not too bad. Nothing's broken.

00:31:05.440 --> 00:31:07.459
Quick, I'll take you to the infirmary.

00:31:07.459 --> 00:31:08.949
Come on.

00:31:09.920 --> 00:31:11.720
Up you go.

00:31:13.113 --> 00:31:14.913
Easy now.

00:31:17.600 --> 00:31:19.880
If anything happens to him,
I'm coming for you.

00:31:20.899 --> 00:31:24.340
September 7, 2000. Sunny.

00:31:24.340 --> 00:31:26.759
That day's match ended in total chaos.

00:31:26.759 --> 00:31:28.864
- Don't take it to heart.
- I heard...

00:31:28.864 --> 00:31:30.960
He Jin stayed on the field
by himself for a long time.

00:31:30.960 --> 00:31:31.945
It's okay, it really wasn't your fault.

00:31:31.945 --> 00:31:34.739
He didn't say another word to us that night.

00:31:35.360 --> 00:31:38.307
Even though Yu Lei's challenge was strange,

00:31:38.307 --> 00:31:41.620
at least his injury wasn't serious.

00:32:00.479 --> 00:32:04.540
Alright, Master Yu, that's enough.

00:32:04.540 --> 00:32:07.820
You've used half a bottle
of medicated oil in one go.

00:32:07.820 --> 00:32:11.500
People will think
you're trying to deep-fry chicken wings.

00:32:12.759 --> 00:32:14.939
Have some sympathy, will you?

00:32:14.939 --> 00:32:16.060
What do you mean, deep-fry chicken wings?

00:32:16.060 --> 00:32:17.719
Can't you see my foot is
swollen like a pig's trotter?

00:32:17.719 --> 00:32:20.479
I don't know, it doesn't look swollen to me.

00:32:20.479 --> 00:32:22.920
It's been several days.

00:32:22.920 --> 00:32:24.300
The swelling must have gone down by now.

00:32:24.300 --> 00:32:27.079
It's a good thing Chen Ke
carried you to the infirmary.

00:32:27.079 --> 00:32:29.399
Who knew he was actually a decent guy?

00:32:32.079 --> 00:32:33.600
You guys don't get it.

00:32:33.600 --> 00:32:36.899
A bone injury takes a hundred days to heal.

00:32:38.120 --> 00:32:39.239
I'm done with you guys.

00:32:39.239 --> 00:32:40.799
I'm going.

00:32:40.799 --> 00:32:42.139
Going where?

00:32:42.139 --> 00:32:43.219
To the bathroom.

00:32:43.219 --> 00:32:46.560
We'll go with you.

00:32:46.560 --> 00:32:47.719
I'm not going to the bathroom!

00:32:47.719 --> 00:32:49.239
- Then where?
- I'm going to the library.

00:32:49.239 --> 00:32:51.540
- Don't be so polite.
- You don't need help?

00:32:51.540 --> 00:32:53.619
You really don't?

00:32:53.619 --> 00:32:55.020
Look at him.

00:32:55.020 --> 00:32:57.260
What is he up to every day?

00:33:25.419 --> 00:33:28.279
What is he doing here?

00:33:28.279 --> 00:33:30.960
Should I say something?

00:33:30.960 --> 00:33:32.460
Yu Lei.

00:33:34.680 --> 00:33:35.860
Is your foot better?

00:33:35.860 --> 00:33:39.120
About last time, I'm really sorry.

00:33:39.120 --> 00:33:40.242
It's no big deal.

00:33:40.242 --> 00:33:42.459
- Really?
- I didn't even give it a second thought.

00:33:42.459 --> 00:33:43.820
Quiet, please.

00:33:43.820 --> 00:33:45.139
If you want to talk, go outside.

00:33:45.139 --> 00:33:47.979
- Sorry.
- Sorry, Professor.

00:33:55.813 --> 00:33:58.174
What's his problem?

00:34:33.531 --> 00:34:36.700
September 14, 2000. Sunny.

00:34:36.700 --> 00:34:40.215
Today, Yu Lei handed me a note.
[Sorry for the trouble on the court!]

00:34:40.215 --> 00:34:44.319
It felt a bit nonsensical,
but also kind of cute.

00:34:44.319 --> 00:34:47.019
- Will we become friends?
- No worries.

00:34:47.019 --> 00:34:50.280
For some reason,
I find myself looking forward to it.

00:34:50.280 --> 00:34:52.099
Are you okay?

00:34:52.099 --> 00:34:53.899
I'm fine.

00:35:14.720 --> 00:35:16.820
There's still the freshman gala.

00:35:16.820 --> 00:35:19.300
I'm definitely going to win that one.

00:35:23.963 --> 00:35:30.440
[Grand Hall]
[Mingde University 2000 Welcoming Gala]

00:35:31.459 --> 00:35:33.340
[Next Episode]
Chen Ke's performance was canceled.

00:35:33.340 --> 00:35:35.379
But why only Chen Ke's?

00:35:35.379 --> 00:35:37.300
Why not anyone else's?

00:35:37.300 --> 00:35:39.499
Why do you think?

00:35:39.499 --> 00:35:40.740
It's rigged!

00:35:40.740 --> 00:35:43.780
Beautiful souls will always
be drawn to each other.

00:35:43.780 --> 00:35:46.660
They'll keep getting closer.

00:35:46.660 --> 00:35:48.199
Just like...

00:35:48.199 --> 00:35:51.579
You're from Yuanmou, Yunnan...

00:35:51.579 --> 00:35:53.816
and I'm from Zhoukoudian, Beijing.

00:35:53.816 --> 00:35:57.020
Can I call you my friend?

00:35:57.020 --> 00:36:00.901
No. My best friend.

00:36:02.950 --> 00:36:11.990
Timing and Subtitles provided to you
by 💥🍥 TEAM 7️⃣ 🍥💥 @viki.com

00:36:15.610 --> 00:36:21.210
♫ Stop asking ♫

00:36:22.070 --> 00:36:29.010
♫ We had clearly agreed on this ♫

00:36:29.660 --> 00:36:36.330
♫ That song you once played for me— ♫

00:36:36.330 --> 00:36:42.040
♫ It remains a faded,
dappled memory of that scorching summer ♫

00:36:43.860 --> 00:36:46.500
♫ Some things simply cannot be forgotten ♫

00:36:46.500 --> 00:36:50.410
♫ Why speak of them anymore? ♫

00:36:50.410 --> 00:36:53.370
♫ Why is it that the more I long for you ♫

00:36:53.370 --> 00:36:57.980
♫ The more my heart aches? ♫

00:36:57.980 --> 00:37:04.900
♫ The winter snow cannot bring back
the stifling heat of those summer nights ♫

00:37:04.900 --> 00:37:11.550
♫ The buzzing of cicadas in my ears
whispers that I remember it all ♫

00:37:11.550 --> 00:37:15.100
♫ Running until we were drenched in sweat— ♫

00:37:15.100 --> 00:37:18.590
♫ You and I once ran side by side ♫

00:37:18.590 --> 00:37:25.760
♫ Now, only silence remains
as we stand face to face— ♫

00:37:25.760 --> 00:37:29.230
♫ And how much reluctance I feel to let go ♫

00:37:29.230 --> 00:37:36.010
♫ Only to repeat the past all over again ♫